New work! Nayaa kaam! 
Been eagerly waiting to share this with you all!! 

For your daughter's baby shower/ Godbharaai, along with diamonds and gold and silver, gift her and her baby health and nutrition. 

My director @veneetrajbagga! Sir thank you for trusting me with your vision! 
My DOP @ikavin who made this film dream-like.
My gorgeous looking producer who bent over backwards to work things out @aanchbhargava. You should be in front of the camera soon, girl. 
My HMU @geetsukhani with the 4kgs of hair extensions. Haha 
My prosthetics team @nagendra and @uzma. You guys have worked tirelessly.
@aratifedane was the most stressed out person in set! But look at what she's made!!
 @madhupourna_official for lending her voice.
My costume designer @pampabis
And of course, @piyushrainacasting @piyuraina @jusst_randomly for being with me at all times.

Let me know what did you think of this beautiful film, in the comments' section.

As you know, I’ve been on a bit of a morning juice- kick lately. This has been my breakfast for the last week and a half and I am telling you, I feel great! 
I kinda fell back into the whole corona diet, eating and drinking a little too much but now I’m back on track.

Does anyone else juice? What is your favourite?

My new favourite is Celery! 
The classic apple, Beet and carrot with ginger and mint remain.

Let me know if you try it! 🥤

latestPosts.caption:
TRUTH TIME - It took me many many years to accept myself wholly. What I could change, I changed- you've seen me at the gym, trekking, swimming, eating right, haven't you? 
What I could not change, now that was tricky. Until I realised that how "I" presented myself is the way the world would view me. 
I had to change my beliefs. Worked very very hard, I tell you. My friends and family are proof of this. 
But baby, once I did, I was liberated. 
Self-love starts with self- kindness. It's beautiful on this side 🙂✨ COME JOIN ME!!

Do you look at the mirror and wish you looked/ appeared slightly different than you do? Share your thoughts with me. Let's chat.

Shruthy Menon is Megha Nambiar
Some memories never fade, some wounds never heal… Megha Nambiar lives with both.
